casebody.data:
PHOENIX MANUF’G CORP., Respondent, v. BARLOW, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by the Phoenix Manufacturing Corporation against Everett D. Barlow.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

Robt. P. Barlow, for appellant. T. D. Kenneson, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with §10 costs and disbursements.
